Ubuntu users can install Smuxi from this [PPA], just run the following
commands:

    sudo add-apt-repository ppa:meebey/smuxi-stable
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install smuxi

Now you can start Smuxi from the Unity Dash.

